  "synopsis": "Star Wars: Crimson Reign is a canon comic-book miniseries and crossover event created by Marvel Comics. It is written by Charles Soule and drawn by Steven Cummings. The story focuses on Crimson Dawn and Qi'ra after the events of Star Wars: War of the Bounty Hunters. The five-part series began publication on December 8, 2021. The series concluded 6 months later in June of 2022",
